Company Description: Founded IN 1948, Mcdonald's Corp. Is One Of The Leading Food Service Retailers IN The World. Located IN Fort Lauderdale, Fla., It Operates More Than 32,000 Outlets IN 117 Countries Serving Around 60 Million Customers Daily. The Restaurant Chain Offers Various Food Items, Including Big Mac, Quarter Pounder, Chicken Mcnuggets And Egg Mcmuffin Along With A Variety Of Beverages. The Chain Also Caters Meal Bundles, Including Dollar Menu, Extra Value Meals, Happy Meals And Mighty Kids Meals For Family And Children. Mcdonald's Corp. Also Provides Special Dishes From Various Cuisines Of The World, Including Brazil, Hong Kong, Italy And Portugal, To Name A Few. It Features IN Fortune Magazine's List Of Most Admired Company IN The World As Well As IN Barron's Magazine's 2010 Annual Survey As Most Respected Company. The Outlet Also Offers Free WI-Fi, Arch Card, Play Places And Party Services.

Founded IN 1955, Mcdonald S Is A Global Food Service Retailer That Operates More Than 30,000 Locations IN Over 100 Countries. The Restaurant Serves Various Shakes, Hamburgers, Grilled And Fried Chicken Products, Salads, Fruits, Sandwiches And Fish. It Additionally Offers French Fries, Chicken Sandwiches, Quarter Pounders And Honey Wheat Rolls. The Restaurant S Menu Also Includes The Ranch Snack Wrap, Big N' Tasty, Chicken Selects And Mcflurry Treats. It Serves A Variety Of Beverages And Desserts, Including Chocolate Triple Thick, Minty Mudd Bath Triple Thick And Strawberry Triple Thick Shakes And Mcdonaldland Cookies. The Restaurant Serves Nearly 50 Million People Each Day. Mcdonald S Restaurants Are Owned And Operated By Independent Franchisees Of Mcdonald's Corporation.
